      "rationale": "MRL 5 demands robust SQA practices. The solver used (OpenFOAM 8) has documented regression testing but lacks formal V&V certification documentation required at Gradation 4. Version control and issue tracking are present; independent code review is partial.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Gradation 4 requires documented SQA plan, regression test suite covering hemolysis-relevant physics, independent code review, and configuration management conforming to a recognized software standard (e.g., IEC 62304 or equivalent). All four sub-elements must be satisfied."
