      "rationale": "The power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) is used without assessment of alternative model forms. Sensitivity to model-form assumptions has not been quantified. Gradation 4 requires demonstrated superiority over alternative model forms via validation evidence."
    },
